<section class="use-case-problem">
  <div class="container container-narrow">
    <div class="use-case-content reveal">
      <h2>The Challenge</h2>
      <p>You've tried before. The gym membership in January. The morning routine that lasted two weeks. The meditation app gathering dust on your phone.</p>
      <p>The problem isn't motivation—you have plenty of that at 11pm when you make the plan. The problem is how you're building:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Starting too big (45-minute workouts when you can barely do 5 minutes)</li>
        <li>Relying on willpower (which depletes throughout the day)</li>
        <li>No accountability (apps don't know if you actually did it)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Every failed attempt makes the next one harder to start.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

